[http://openlabtools.eng.cam.ac.uk/index.php OpenLabTools]  is a University of Cambridge initiative, which aims to provide a forum and knowledge centre for the development of low cost and open access scientific tools, with an emphasis on undergraduate and graduate teaching and research.

This page shows [[open source]] scientific hardware, which can be used to make [[open source labs]] developed by [http://openlabtools.eng.cam.ac.uk/index.php OpenLabTools].

